{"tid":1025049,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨眼小馬半夜被騎走 「策騎者」竟然係一隻狗","createTime":"2019-02-17T05:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T05:22:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5568faec32889ea45919addddc4df8aab5cc7b4","tid":1025049,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550224424_82be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550224424_82be.jpg&h=c1dd17d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190215/large/1550224424_2dbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190215%2Flarge%2F1550224424_2dbb.jpg&h=9dbdb043&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哥基騎在小馬背上<br />\n美國密蘇里州一隻獨眼小馬在黑暗的小路中慢慢前行，似乎被甚麼東西「引領」着，牠的22歲女主人上前查看之下，不禁好氣又好笑，原來是鄰居的哥基犬騎在自家小馬背上，她拍下這個畫面跟網友分享。<br />\n事緣主人申克爾（Callie Schenker）回家後，驚見她家中盲了一隻眼的小馬被某些「東西」騎走。她仔細查看，發現騎在小馬背上原來是鄰居的哥基犬，申克爾忍不住笑了起來。她拍下這有趣的一刻，可見小馬在黑暗中踱步，哥基犬則坐在牠背上。<br />\n申克爾把片段上載到社交網Facebook，寫道：「我沒有編造這件事，我們今晚回到馬路上就見到這情景了。這不是我家的狗，但明顯，他和獨眼小馬『Cricket』是很好的朋友。」申克爾說：「狗狗沒有受傷。狗狗在家中沒有被欺凌，他只是喜愛在我們居住的鄉郊地區四處遊走。」她補充：「『Cricket』沒有大礙，牠很久前因意外失去了一隻眼，但與狗狗沒有關係。我沒有放狗狗在小馬背上。」<br />\n隨後，申克爾再上載另一條在日間拍攝的短片，更清楚見到哥基圍着「Cricket」跳躍，嘗試了數次後成功騎在牠身上。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190217/59263099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59263099&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxnza4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=655baac4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190217%2F59263099&h=8d4d8bb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190217/59263099</a>"},{"pid":"e2f1ab3bf93fd2b91db73f3739fde74ffca86f6e","tid":1025049,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98613f6d0d48dca0252641b79ee7b84aae03f2a","tid":1025049,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:22:38.000Z","msg":"馬達加斯加<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}